# Assets Images Directory

This directory will contain all game images including:
- background.png
- ui_frame.png
- faction icons (faction_sword.png, faction_shield.png, faction_spear.png)
- card images (card_rock.png, card_paper.png, card_scissors.png, card_back.png)
- effect icons (icon_armor.png, icon_enhanced_glow.png)
